{"tid":1676591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實會唔會搞個要求雙普選既遊行或集會？","createTime":"2019-10-26T14:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T06:22:40.000Z","uid":34409,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"caa3e01c3e5ec760e7741c16f4325ab47abdd0f3","tid":1676591,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"係五大訴求中，有一項一直都被忽略，<br />\n無論遊行或文宣都少提及的，<br />\n就係全面落實雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n只要一日冇普選，政府既服務對象都唔係香港巿民。<br />\n而我相信只要有普選，<br />\n其他幾個訴求先有行使既可能。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係，其實美國《香港人權和民主法案》中，<br />\n其實都有提及需限時給予香港有普選，<br />\n所以搞一次要求有雙普選既集會或遊行，<br />\n係可以向國際提出一個回應，<br />\n我地需要普選既必要。"},{"pid":"4b0d31f14722c4e22b7844e33c4da980d5332fab","tid":1676591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:20:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"78c1b0e798e173fc14de1339f803143709e0fdc8","tid":1676591,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fjD4oa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fjD4oa.jpg&h=9706368f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpEQa3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpEQa3b.jpg&h=838831f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2naVuR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2naVuR.jpg&h=f43d87f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShUgQ3d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShUgQ3d.gif&h=fb0ac362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f56950ab97254e34fe81e454bf46ef1c9b4cd19","tid":1676591,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n仲有新疆"},{"pid":"8a9de945fc39264ddc73a393cd0f47c61911005e","tid":1676591,"uid":34409,"like":0,"disli